  "texts": [
    "It not only deepens the GNN's knowledge of chemical molecular structure but also significantly improves the model's generalization ability in various chemical prediction tasks, highlighting the great potential of integrating physics principles with machine learning model design.",
    "Meanwhile, (Xu et al. 2024) introduced MESPool, an innovative edgecontraction pooling method, which changes the traditional atom-centered pooling mode and focuses on chemical bonds or edges as the basic unit of information aggregation.",
    "By simulating the construction mechanism of a scaffold tree (Schuffenhauer et al. 2007), MESPool can effectively retain the key connection information in the molecular graph.",
    "With the deepening of the network layers, functional groups are gradually refined into super-nodes, thus demonstrating extraordinary performance in ADT prediction.",
    "In ADT prediction, (Ma et al. 2024) introduced a multi-view graph pooling technique."
  ],
